-- 2010-11-20T12:14:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-20/iran-is-main-missile-threat-to-europe-france-s-sarkozy-tells-nato-summit.html
French President Nicolas Sarkozy
said Iran poses the main missile threat to Europe. He spoke to
reporters in Lisbon today after NATO approved a missile-defense
plan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
